<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Expense Tracker</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #FF9F00;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            color: #0288D1;
        }
        .navbar .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #FF9F00, #FF5722);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .hero .btn-primary {
            background-color: #03A9F4;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .hero .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0288D1;
        }
        .hero .img-fluid {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .services, .benefits {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }
        .services h2, .benefits h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .services .row, .benefits .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }
        .services .service-card, .benefits .benefit-card {
            text-align: center;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .services .service-card:hover, .benefits .benefit-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .services .icon, .benefits .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #FF9F00;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .contact-us {
            background-color: #FF9F00;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }
        .contact-us h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .contact-us form {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .contact-us input, .contact-us textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .contact-us button {
            background-color: #03A9F4;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .contact-us button:hover {
            background-color: #0288D1;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #FF9F00;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Expense Tracker</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#services">Services</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#benefits">Benefits</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#contact-us">Contact Us</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h1 class="display-4">Take Control of Your Finances</h1>
                    <p class="lead">Track your expenses, manage loans, and get timely reminders to stay on top of your financial goals. Simplifying money management, one step at a time.</p>
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Started</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="https://cdn3d.iconscout.com/3d/premium/thumb/online-expensive-report-3d-icon-download-in-png-blend-fbx-gltf-file-formats--expenses-tracker-neo-banking-pack-finance-icons-5727732.png" alt="Expense Tracker" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section id="services" class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Services We Offer</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-wallet2 icon"></i>
                        <h4>Manage Your Spending</h4>
                        <p>Track your daily, weekly, and monthly expenses with ease and see where your money goes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow icon"></i>
                        <h4>Top 5 Spending Categories</h4>
                        <p>View your top 5 high-usage spending categories in an easy-to-read donut chart.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-cash-stack icon"></i>
                        <h4>Loan & Repayment Tracking</h4>
                        <p>Monitor loans, track payments, and get monthly reminders for upcoming due dates.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="benefits" class="benefits">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Benefits of Using Expense Tracker</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle icon"></i>
                        <h4>Financial Awareness</h4>
                        <p>Stay informed about where your money is going, allowing you to make smarter spending decisions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-clock icon"></i>
                        <h4>Timely Reminders</h4>
                        <p>Receive timely reminders for loan payments and upcoming expenses, ensuring you never miss a due date.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-save icon"></i>
                        <h4>Save Money</h4>
                        <p>By identifying wasteful spending, our app helps you save an average of 15% on monthly expenditures.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="contact-us" class="contact-us">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <form action="/" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Expense Tracker. All Rights Reserved. | <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
